Package: definer
Title: Makes it easy to apply field maps / survey data definitions to datasets with integer coding
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Adam",
           family = "Davis",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "davisadamw@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6324-6380"))
Description: 
    Survey data is often delivered with categorical variables coded as integers. 
    This saves a lot of space but can make analysis pretty painful. This package helps 
    you use a recode / definitions table to update values of variables painlessly.
